# Smart Contracts (contracts/)

## Guidelines

- Use Solidity for Ethereum smart contracts
- Follow best practices for security (checks-effects-interactions pattern)
- Include comprehensive comments explaining contract logic
- Implement proper access control
- Add events for important state changes
- Optimize for gas efficiency
- Include test files for all contracts
- Document contract interfaces and deployment procedures
